@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #82954 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?

P-medium seems fine, I don't know why you would need to have an instance of this type - even for variance you can just use two different PhantomDatas: https://play.rust-lang.org/?version=nightly&mode=debug&edition=2018&gist=4cd67b4975546d77b1667b7895e4ce13
agreed on p-medium, it's also an old issue (which is probably the reason why it lingered for 2 years unnoticed)
